direction: right
classes: {
  node: {
    shape: rectangle
    style: {
      fill: "#f4f4f4"
      stroke: "#333333"
      font-size: 28
      bold: true
      border-radius: 5
    }
  }
}

Context: Context\nMultiple LLM providers exist\nwith different API structures. {
  class: node
  style: { fill: "#e3f2fd"; stroke: "#1e88e5" }
}

Decision: Decision\nImplement a Unified LLM Interface\n(argus.core.llm) {
  class: node
  style: { fill: "#e8f5e9"; stroke: "#43a047" }
}

Options: Options Considered\n1. Direct API calls (Rejected)\n2. Unified Interface (Accepted) {
  class: node
  style: { fill: "#fff3e0"; stroke: "#fb8c00" }
}

Consequences: Consequences\n+ Easy to switch providers\n+ Consistent agent logic\n- Maintenance overhead for new APIs {
  class: node
  style: { fill: "#fce4ec"; stroke: "#d81b60" }
}

Context -> Options: leads to { style: { font-size: 22; stroke-width: 4 } }
Options -> Decision: resolves to { style: { font-size: 22; stroke-width: 4 } }
Decision -> Consequences: results in { style: { font-size: 22; stroke-width: 4 } }
